OL,5, Parliament's expenses watchdog is      
OL,6, facing a backlash from MPs after it    
OL,7, told them they can claim for the cost  
OL,8, of an office Christmas party.          
OL,10,FThe Independent Parliamentary Standards
OL,11,FAuthority (Ipsa) announced MPs can this
OL,12,Fyear claim for food, decorations and   
OL,13,Fnon-alcoholic drinks.                  
OL,15,FBut MPs on all sides have rejected the 
OL,16,Fguidance, with one calling it "bonkers"
OL,17,Famid a cost of living crisis.          
OL,19,FIpsa said holding a "modest gathering" 
OL,20,Ffor staff was "entirely appropriate".  
